{"tid":315353,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"分享)   動物傳心師好勁,隻龜去左邊都知道..","createTime":"2017-07-10T03:18:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T09:22:08.000Z","uid":82845,"like":73,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"85ed627ccf809b2ae96a1639ee2603ce0712d062","tid":315353,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T03:18:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/program/122490332/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fprogram%2F122490332%2F&d=SNSQihyh%2Fj3X1%2BENQWX1JSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=f8c4bb41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fprogram%2F122490332%2F&h=34ae3a1b\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/program/122490332/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.cc/i2/YXLa2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FYXLa2b.jpg&h=538df89b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近《新聞刺針》記者的寵物烏龜走失，看見動物傳心大行其道。有引用量子物理原理的傳心師，亦有用腦電波的。<span style=\"color: red;\">他們都說靠動物照片就能知道動物想甚麼</span>，於是記者決定一試。<br />\n<br />\n有線記者send左張玩具龜既相, 俾5個所謂「動物傳心師」, 個個都話同隻「龜」傾到計, 問到隻「龜」點解走, 最神奇係見到隻「龜」而家睇緊乜<br />\n<br />\n不過咁樣「傾計」原來要收幾百蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c3652dc4eabd1a6f1c917d3e48aefa74eced07","tid":315353,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T03:18:56.000Z","msg":"最尾d傳心師反應笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cad6d745efa5e1295675b13c4979f6aaaad6e4b","tid":315353,"uid":16453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-1